---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<div class="section-container">
  <div class="description-section">
    <h2 class="section-heading">Join Nepal Climate Hub</h2>
    <div class="introduction-section">
      <p>
        We are looking to onboard our first batch of volunteer Operating Team
        members to help propel Nepal Climate Hub forward.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our mission is to educate, connect, and empower Nepal’s young people
        with timely information, resources, networking opportunities, and
        practical guidance to address pressing climate challenges through
        individual and collective action.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you have a deep understanding and passion for climate change and
        solutions in Nepal and want to leverage your knowledge and skills to
        educate, inspire, and mobilize youth across Nepal, we invite you to join
        us.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-volunteer-section sub-section">
      <h3 class="sub-heading">Why volunteer with us?</h3>
      <p>
        Volunteering with Nepal Climate Hub as a member of our first Operating
        Teams offers a unique opportunity to gain hands-on experience in
        nonprofit leadership and operations while making a meaningful
        contribution to climate action in Nepal. Here’s what you’ll gain:
      </p>
      <ul class="volunteering-list">
        <li>
          <span class="description-term"
            ><strong>Content Knowledge</strong></span
          >: Deepen your understanding of climate issues facing Nepal, as well
          as the activists, researchers, and organizations working to advance
          policy change and develop and deploy effective solutions.
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="description-term"
            ><strong>Skill Development</strong></span
          >: Gain and practice new skills in copywriting, social media and
          content management, software engineering, branding, project
          management, design, and more.
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="description-term"
            ><strong>Networking Opportunities</strong></span
          >: Connect with like-minded individuals and organizations passionate
          about climate action.
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="description-term"><strong>Community Impact</strong></span
          >: Play a direct role in educating and empowering thousands of youth
          across Nepal to make a meaningful difference in their communities.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="eligibilty-section sub-section">
      <h3 class="sub-heading">Eligibility</h3>
      <p>
        We are seeking students and young professionals who are passionate about
        climate action and committed to growing the impact and reach of Nepal
        Climate Hub.
      </p>

      <>
        <b>Time commitment</b>: 10-12 hrs/week
      </>

      <!-- <p class="note">
        Volunteer roles opening soon! Follow us for updates and start
        contributing now on our <a href="/contribute">Contribute</a> page.
      </p> -->
    </div>

    <div class="open-roles-section sub-section">
      <h3 class="sub-heading">Open Roles</h3>
      <p>
        We are seeking creative, purpose-driven people for the following roles:
      </p>
      <div class="roles-grid">
        <!-- Video Editor -->
        <article class="role-card" data-role="video-editor" data-openings="1">
          <h4 class="role-title">
            Video Editor <span class="role-openings">(1)</span>
          </h4>
          <p class="role-intro">
            Help us bring climate change stories to life! We’re looking for a
            creative video editor to produce short, engaging reels and videos
            that educate, inspire, and connect audiences to climate change
            issues.
          </p>

          <h5 class="responsibility">What you’ll do</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Edit short-form videos and reels for social media platforms.
            </li>
            <li>
              Turn climate facts and stories into compelling visual narratives.
            </li>
            <li>
              Work closely with our team to ensure a consistent style and
              impactful messaging.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h5 class="requirements">What we’re looking for</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>A knack for storytelling through video.</li>
            <li>
              Basic editing skills (any editing software you’re comfortable
              with).
            </li>
            <li>Passion for climate change awareness and youth engagement.</li>
          </ul>

          <p class="role-apply">
            Application link: <a
              href="https://forms.gle/P2VEUBQMdie3rgp56"
              target="_blank"
              aria-label="Apply for Video Editor role">Apply now</a
            >
          </p>
        </article>

        <!-- Climate Storyteller -->
        <article
          class="role-card"
          data-role="climate-storyteller"
          data-openings="1"
        >
          <h4 class="role-title">
            Climate Storyteller <span class="role-openings">(1)</span>
          </h4>
          <p class="role-intro">
            We’re looking for a storyteller who can turn climate facts and
            topics into compelling narratives that inspire action and connect
            with audiences on an emotional level.
          </p>

          <h5 class="responsibility">What you’ll do</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Research climate change topics, facts, and trends.</li>
            <li>
              Craft engaging narratives for articles, social media posts, and
              campaigns.
            </li>
            <li>
              Collaborate with our video editors, writers, and designers to
              ensure stories align with our mission and resonate with youth
              audiences.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h5 class="requirements">What we’re looking for</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Strong writing skills and a passion for narrative storytelling.
            </li>
            <li>
              Ability to simplify complex climate topics for a general audience.
            </li>
            <li>Passion for climate change awareness and youth engagement.</li>
          </ul>

          <p class="role-apply">
            Application link: <a
              href="https://forms.gle/P2VEUBQMdie3rgp56"
              target="_blank"
              aria-label="Apply for Climate Storyteller role">Apply now</a
            >
          </p>
        </article>

        <!-- UI/UX Designer -->
        <article class="role-card" data-role="ui-ux-designer" data-openings="2">
          <h4 class="role-title">
            UI/UX Designer <span class="role-openings">(2)</span>
          </h4>
          <p class="role-intro">
            We’re looking for a creative and mission-driven UI/UX designer to
            craft intuitive, engaging, and impactful designs for our platform,
            social media, and digital campaigns.
          </p>

          <h5 class="responsibility">What you’ll do</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Design user-friendly interfaces for web and mobile platforms.
            </li>
            <li>
              Create wireframes, mockups, and prototypes to bring ideas to life.
            </li>
            <li>
              Collaborate with our content, storytelling, and development teams
              to ensure a seamless user journey.
            </li>
            <li>
              Use design to make climate change information accessible,
              engaging, and action-oriented.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h5 class="requirements">What we’re looking for</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Experience with design tools (Figma, Adobe XD, or similar).</li>
            <li>Understanding of user-centered design principles.</li>
            <li>
              Creativity, attention to detail, and a collaborative mindset.
            </li>
            <li>Passion for climate change awareness and empowering youth.</li>
          </ul>

          <p class="role-apply">
            Application link: <a
              href="https://forms.gle/P2VEUBQMdie3rgp56"
              target="_blank"
              aria-label="Apply for UI/UX Designer role">Apply now</a
            >
          </p>
        </article>

        <!-- Creative Writer -->
        <article
          class="role-card"
          data-role="creative-writer"
          data-openings="1"
        >
          <h4 class="role-title">
            Creative Writer <span class="role-openings">(1)</span>
          </h4>
          <p class="role-intro">
            We’re looking for a creative writer to turn climate ideas into words
            that educate, inspire, and spark action. Your writing will help our
            audience connect with climate change issues on both an intellectual
            and emotional level.
          </p>

          <h5 class="responsibility">What you’ll do</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Write engaging content for blogs, newsletters, social media, and
              campaigns.
            </li>
            <li>Adapt complex climate facts into clear, relatable language.</li>
            <li>
              Collaborate with storytellers, editors, and designers to align
              tone, style, and message.
            </li>
            <li>
              Contribute ideas for creative campaigns and awareness initiatives.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h5 class="requirements">What we’re looking for</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Strong writing and editing skills.</li>
            <li>
              Ability to adjust writing style for different audiences and
              platforms.
            </li>
            <li>Creativity and curiosity about climate topics.</li>
            <li>Passion for climate change awareness and youth engagement.</li>
          </ul>

          <p class="role-apply">
            Application link: <a
              href="https://forms.gle/P2VEUBQMdie3rgp56"
              target="_blank"
              aria-label="Apply for Creative Writer role">Apply now</a
            >
          </p>
        </article>

        <!-- Editor -->
        <article class="role-card" data-role="editor" data-openings="1">
          <h4 class="role-title">
            Content Editor <span class="role-openings">(1)</span>
          </h4>
          <p class="role-intro">
            We’re looking for an editor who carefully refines content to create
            clear, engaging stories that raise awareness about climate change.
          </p>

          <h5 class="responsibility">What you’ll do</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Meticulously edit articles, reports, social media posts, and
              campaign materials.
            </li>
            <li>
              Ensure clarity, accuracy, and consistent tone across all content.
            </li>
            <li>
              Collaborate closely with writers, storytellers, and designers to
              elevate their work.
            </li>
            <li>
              Help maintain our brand voice while making complex climate topics
              accessible and compelling.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h5 class="requirements">What we’re looking for</h5>
          <ul>
            <li>Exceptional command of language and grammar.</li>
            <li>A keen eye for detail and a passion for quality.</li>
            <li>Experience editing diverse content formats.</li>
            <li>
              Passion for climate change communication and youth engagement.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <p class="role-apply">
            Application link: <a
              href="https://forms.gle/P2VEUBQMdie3rgp56"
              aria-label="Apply for Editor role"
              target="_blank">Apply now</a
            >
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .section-container {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 48px auto 0px;
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .introduction-section {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .introduction-section p {
    line-height: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .sub-heading {
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .sub-section p {
    line-height: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  ul.volunteering-list {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  ul.volunteering-list li {
    list-style-type: none;
    line-height: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  ul.roles-list .description-term {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  ul.roles-list > li {
    list-style-position: inside;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  ul.roles-list ul li {
    margin-left: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .eligibilty-section {
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .note {
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 24px;
    color: blue;
  }

  .open-roles-section {
    margin-top: -32px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .role-title {
    font-size: 20px;
  }

  .role-title,
  .responsibility,
  .requirements {
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .role-card ul {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .role-card {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .role-card li {
    list-style-type: disc;
    list-style-position: inside;
  }

  .role-apply a {
    color: blue;
  }

  /* style for responsiveness */

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-container {
      margin: 24px 24px 32px;
    }
  }
</style>
